### 1. Créer le Coach de Surf
POST http://localhost:8080/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nom": "Slater",
  "prenom": "Kelly",
  "email": "kelly.coach@slideit.com",
  "role": "MONITEUR",
  "telephone": "0611223344"
}

###

### 2. Créer l'Élève
POST http://localhost:8080/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nom": "Dupont",
  "prenom": "Jean",
  "email": "jean.eleve@email.com",
  "role": "ELEVE",
