}

###

### 3. Planifier la Session de Surf
POST http://localhost:8080/api/sessions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "discipline": "SURF",
  "dateHeureDebut": "2026-06-01T10:00:00",
  "dateHeureFin": "2026-06-01T12:00:00",
  "statut": "PLANIFIEE",
  "coach": { "id": 1 },
  "eleve": { "id": 2 }
}